<p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(238, 243, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">会议指出，寒潮天气防范和寒假期间安全稳定工作关系到学院师生的生命安全和学院正常教育教学秩序，学院各职能部门负责人、辅导员要高度重视，加强领导，明确责任，确保各项工作落到实处。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(238, 243, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">经济管理学院党总支书记蔡书记要求，各辅导员要进一步提高站位，强化责任意识一是要加强寒潮天气的监测预警，及时发布相关信息，确保学生了解天气变化；二是做好防寒保暖工作，对学院设施进行检查维护，确保水电设施安全运行；三是要加强安全教育，提高学生和老师的自我保护意识，特别是加强对学生的安全教育，防止意外事故的发生；四是要督促提醒师生离校要断水断电。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(238, 243, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">会议还对寒假期间学院安全稳定工作进行了部署。一要加强对师生的思想政治工作，加强寒假期间意识形态领域安全稳定；二要定时在学生和家长群里进行温馨提示，提醒学生和家长做好防寒潮，确保家人和学生的个人安全，三要加强对学院实验室、宿舍等场所的安全检查，确保寒假期间校园安全稳定；四要确保寒假期间信息畅通，及时应对突发事件。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(238, 243, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">会议最后强调，各负责人要密切协作，形成合力，切实加强对寒潮天气防范和寒假期间安全稳定工作的组织领导，确保学院师生度过一个安全、稳定的寒假。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240417/1713366645510066722.png" title="1713366645510066722.png" alt="image.png" width="495" height="328" style="width: 495px; height: 328px;"/></p>